OL,6,FA teacher who urged a girl to send him
OL,7,Fan indecent photograph and then shared
OL,8,Fit with another child when she refused
OL,9,Fto give him any more has been jailed.
OL,11,FWest Yorkshire teacher Michael Pierce,
OL,12,F32, posed as a 16-year-old boy from
OL,13,FLeeds and befriended his victims via
OL,14,FSnapchat, a court heard.
OL,16,FHe convinced one of the girls to send
OL,17,Fhim a nude photograph.
