OL,6,FPierce, of Blackstone Drive,
OL,7,FShireoaks, Worksop, pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fcausing a child under 13 to engage in
OL,9,Fsexual activity, causing a child to
OL,10,Fwatch a sexual act, inciting a child
OL,11,Funder 13 to engage in sexual activity
OL,12,Fand distributing an indecent
OL,13,Fphotograph of a child.
OL,15,FAppearing at Leeds Crown Court he was
OL,16,Fjailed for six years and put on the
