OL,6,FDet Sgt Steven Sayles, of Wakefield
OL,7,FDistrict Child Vulnerable to
OL,8,FExploitation Team, said: "This man,
OL,9,Fwho occupied a position of trust, has
OL,10,Ftargeted young girls and used
OL,11,Fthreatening behaviour to try and
OL,12,Fexploit them into sending indecent
OL,13,Fimages.
OL,15,F"The nature of his crimes was
OL,16,Fparticularly concerning given his role
